---
import { site } from '../content/site';
---
<section class="support-block">
  <h2>Need Help?</h2>
  <p>For account requests, technical issues, software requests, or questions about Research Computing services, email <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a> or open a ticket at <a href={site.ticketUrl}>request.fandm.edu</a>.</p>
  <p><strong>When opening a ticket, include:</strong> your username, the service involved, the course or project if applicable, screenshots, error messages, and the steps you already tried.</p>
</section>
